Functions to:

- validate ISBN-10, ISBN-13 and EAN barcodes;

- convert between ISBN-10 and ISBN-13 (both ways);

- obtain the market or language from a small subset of ISBN prefixes,
  focusing at this time on ISBN prefixes used in the Americas and Europe;

Contributions to extend and improve this library are very welcome.

Tested with:

- cPython 2.6, 2.7
- cPython 3.2
- Pypy 1.7 (2.7)
- Jython 2.5.2

This library is hereby placed in the public domain.

